{"id": "1301763261343072309", "channel_id": "1288131612063825920", "type": 19, "author_id": "800269534521983028", "author_name": "lazydoge_", "author_bot": false, "content": "唉，如果当初福袋事件能多听玩家意见，不那么倔，或许结局会不一样...事实证明小体量游戏得罪那么多玩家没有活路，还是二游削卡这种碰都不能碰的底线，事到如今又把福袋回调，何必当初呢", "timestamp": "2024-11-01T04:22:27.096000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1301574401858207805", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1288131612063825920", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "哈基米 我也想長大一下", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1301795532364316703", "channel_id": "1288131612063825920", "type": 0, "author_id": "283528782911111168", "author_name": "deadinside3850", "author_bot": false, "content": "你补药④啊 我才刚入坑 💀", "timestamp": "2024-11-01T06:30:41.107000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1288131612063825920", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "哈基米 我也想長大一下", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1301796575273680946", "channel_id": "1288131612063825920", "type": 19, "author_id": "299947644208414720", "author_name": "cs001092", "author_bot": false, "content": "这坑是有点难度<:Coffee:1240919421791375380>", "timestamp": "2024-11-01T06:34:49.756000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["283528782911111168"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1301795532364316703", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1288131612063825920", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "哈基米 我也想長大一下", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1301813738457792543", "channel_id": "1288131612063825920", "type": 19, "author_id": "701773206255567010", "author_name": "r3pk1r0nca", "author_bot": false, "content": "但其實我覺得在那個背景下，削弱是合情合理的，誰也不想看到一個遊戲出現無腦隨便碾的流派吧，越容易達成的事情反而成就感越低\n\n只是後面反擊轉傷那些流派崛起，說要把這些削弱下去又不太實際 ( 如同你所言，沒那個資本了 )，才出現融災、加固這種東西。大家都越來越膨脹的情況下，當初的削弱反而顯得多餘", "timestamp": "2024-11-01T07:43:01.778000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["800269534521983028"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1301763261343072309", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1288131612063825920", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "哈基米 我也想長大一下", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1301814623716114453", "channel_id": "1288131612063825920", "type": 0, "author_id": "701773206255567010", "author_name": "r3pk1r0nca", "author_bot": false, "content": "就是，怎麼講，我個人滿樂見把太突出的角色砍下去 ( 當然會有人不接受而退遊，機會成本極大 )。當突出者沒被砍，反而選擇把敵人提到相同高度時，像在拿遊戲的壽命換玩家的留存，一直無腦提高的下場，就是像神魔那般，角色很快過期、舊角打不起來\n\n而且還會有一坨人吵著要把舊角能力往上拉，拉得跟原本突出那隻一樣，跟目前處境滿像的", "timestamp": "2024-11-01T07:46:32.840000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1288131612063825920", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "哈基米 我也想長大一下", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1301825294340194345", "channel_id": "1288131612063825920", "type": 19, "author_id": "557599119401811978", "author_name": "heikwok", "author_bot": false, "content": "只能說當時的削弱方向不對，角色一直出新的強度早晚會膨脹，總是削弱角色只會讓玩家反感 與其針對角色本身調整倒不如像現在這樣增加怪物機制或提升難度，舊角版本落後打不過也可以再調整加強 而且像福袋這種狀況，最簡單就是縮減關卡長度減少道中的怪物數量，甚至後面有些活動都直接進王關了，沒小怪福袋壓根就無法疊傷，也不影響其他角色發揮", "timestamp": "2024-11-01T08:28:56.915000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["701773206255567010"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1301813738457792543", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1288131612063825920", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "哈基米 我也想長大一下", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1301840100782768180", "channel_id": "1288131612063825920", "type": 19, "author_id": "1079677800023347250", "author_name": "juzi6912", "author_bot": false, "content": "怪物機制和難度提升某玩家群體又要說太難🤡", "timestamp": "2024-11-01T09:27:47.046000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["557599119401811978"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1301825294340194345", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1288131612063825920", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "哈基米 我也想長大一下", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1301841273124163586", "channel_id": "1288131612063825920", "type": 19, "author_id": "557599119401811978", "author_name": "heikwok", "author_bot": false, "content": "難度高而已總沒有事件嚴重 反正把握好分寸就行，血希那隻冰凍的不是也下修過了", "timestamp": "2024-11-01T09:32:26.554000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1079677800023347250"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1301840100782768180", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1288131612063825920", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "哈基米 我也想長大一下", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
